Anomalous access

Login events (with source IPs and Geolocation)

Failed and successful

API and user

Session Hijack

Fast travel events

Suspicious IP

Suspicious user agent

Use of breakglass/local SF accounts

Multiple successive failed logins

Data Theft/Loss

Access events (authorised and unauthorised)

High number of unauthorised access events for a user would be deemed suspicious

Data/File export/download

Bulk API data request

Bulk deletion operations

Privilege Escalation events

New account creation

Permission Modifications

Account disabled/enabled events

Security policy changes

Disabling MFA on accounts

Disabling audit logging

Disabling Data Masking

Changes to access control settings
